The Cost Analysis
We worked out that most of these are free or near-free:

At launch: $0/month (all free tiers)
At 50 customers: ~$85/month
At 200 customers: ~$500/month

The key insight was that users connect their own QuickBooks/Dropbox accounts, so you don't pay for those subscriptions - they do.

