Material suppliers - Home Depot Pro, Lowe's Pro, Ferguson, Grainger - contractors constantly order materials and having direct ordering from the app would save time. 3. Equipment rental - United Rentals, Sunbelt Rentals - crews need equipment on-site and integrating rental platforms could streamline procurement. 4. Insurance/bonding - Certificate of insurance management systems would help track compliance requirements. 5. Permit systems - City permit portals vary by location but integration could automate permit tracking and status updates. 6. Safety/compliance - OSHA apps and safety training platforms keep crews compliant and documented. 7. Fleet/vehicle tracking - Verizon Connect, Samsara, GPS trackers help manage crew locations and vehicle maintenance. 8. Payroll - Direct payroll integration would close the loop on labor tracking.

